Attorney General Jeff Sessions walks away after holding a press conference at the Justice Department in Washington, D.C, on March 2, 2017. (Photo: NICHOLAS KAMM, AFP/Getty Images) 
Bless Merriam-Webster for keeping us up to date on what's on people's minds. 
According to the dictionary, searches for the word "recuse" were up 45,000% on Thursday, as word spread that Attorney General Jeff Sessions met with the Russian ambassador to the United States twice last year. Lookups for 'recuse' are up 45,000%. https://t.co/vJZdYZgAF5
